{"tid":1161504,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大，越anti-social ，係咪正常？","createTime":"2019-05-19T08:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T09:08:00.000Z","uid":123335,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"501f26608579093ee190dec83cad2b58e3f307f9","tid":1161504,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T08:45:45.000Z","msg":"想當年讀大學 <br />\n樂於參加唔同嘅society <br />\n不斷認識唔同範疇、 唔同國籍嘅人<br />\n心諗：「識人好過識字？我兩樣都有，問你死未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而出到嚟社會工作<br />\n荒謬嘅社會扼殺咗生活<br />\n工作、OT、進修既壓力將你寶貴嘅廿四小時渣滓得一乾二淨<br />\n以前識落嘅大部份人，冇時間去keep<br />\n結果，連 hi-bye friend都不如<br />\n如同陌路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你曾經付出過嘅時間，猶如全部白費<br />\n呢一種失落感，唔知有冇人明 ......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以而家已經唔想再好似以前咁識大量嘅人<br />\n識完又 keep 唔到 <br />\n識黎把撚咩屌"},{"pid":"375c465104e950354bbf7c8f18358491aaf6d67f","tid":1161504,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"生活痛苦貧窮下賤既人先會反社會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1161125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1161125</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7ae6d269d5a8f4a973c38b8b0e3f54babd67f3c2","tid":1161504,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"375c465104e950354bbf7c8f18358491aaf6d67f","tid":1161504,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"生活痛苦貧窮下賤既人先會反社會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1161125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1161125</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T08:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e55be209030e992cfa63db5bcaeae293748993c","tid":1161504,"uid":123633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T08:51:12.000Z","msg":"其實同銀行借錢cold call一樣<br />\n你同一百條友social完 有一個幫到你其實已經賺左<br />\n另外果99個 就由鳩佢啦 你估真係付出幾多就收獲幾多咩"},{"pid":"08f9e6